I remember after the Denial of Franchise, Hindi daw kawalan ang ABSCBN Regional Network Group. MGA 70ng ULOL! Tingnan mo nagiging blackout news ang cagayan. Buti na lang nagpatrending sila.

Inaabisuhan naman ang mga residente na magbukas ng mga flashlights o gumawa ng anumang aksyon upang madaling matunton ang kanilang kinaroroonan dahil hirap ang mga rescuers na matunton ang kanilang eksaktong lugar buhat ng malawakang blackout sa lalawigan.

There was a small blackout in NYC.  I got to NYU history dept.  Opening party cancelled.  Walked home the 5 miles or so to the Upper West Side.  I don't remember why I didn't take the bus.  Maybe no room and it was faster to walk?
This was not one of the big deal NYC blackouts. https://t.co/wLq7wafhaN
